# CheckSwing is a single-page app with hash-based routing (#/owner/<slug>,
# #/cycle/<year>, etc.). Hash fragments never reach the server, so no
# server-side rewrite is needed for client-side routes.
#
# This file exists so future redirects (e.g., short URLs, renamed pages)
# have a documented home.

# Example future redirects:
# /old-path  /new-path  301
